#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:5
msgid "Download Sources"
msgstr "模型來源"

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:7
msgid "Xinference supports downloading various models from different sources."
msgstr "Xinference 支援從不同的來源下載各種模型。"

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:10
msgid "HuggingFace"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:11
msgid ""
"Xinference directly downloads the required models from the official `Hugging"
" Face model repository <https://huggingface.co/models>`_ by default."
msgstr ""
"Xinference 預設直接從 `Hugging Face 官方模型倉庫 <https://huggingface.co/models>`_ "
"下載所需的模型。"

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:14
msgid ""
"If you have trouble connecting to Huggingface, you can use a mirror website "
"to download with setting the environment variable ``HF_ENDPOINT=https://hf-"
"mirror.com``."
msgstr ""
"如果你的網路無法連接到 HuggingFace ，你可以透過環境變數指定 HuggingFace "
"鏡像網站：``HF_ENDPOINT=https://hf-mirror.com`` 。"

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:18
msgid "ModelScope"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:20
msgid ""
"When Xinference detects that the system's language is set to Simplified "
"Chinese, it will automatically set the model download source to `ModelScope "
"<https://modelscope.cn/models>`_."
msgstr ""
"當 Xinference 偵測到系統語言設定為「簡體中文」時，會將模型下載來源設為 `ModelScope "
"<https://modelscope.cn/models>`_。"

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:23
msgid ""
"You can also achieve this by manually setting an environment variable "
"``XINFERENCE_MODEL_SRC=modelscope``."
msgstr "你也可以透過手動設定環境變數 ``XINFERENCE_MODEL_SRC=modelscope`` 來實現這一點。"

#: ../../source/models/sources/sources.rst:25
msgid ""
"Please check the detail page of a model to confirm whether the model "
"supports downloading from ModelScope. If a model spec supports downloading "
"from ModelScope, the \"Model Hubs\" section in the spec information will "
"include \"ModelScope\"."
msgstr ""
"請在模型的詳情頁面上查看它是否支援從 ModelScope 進行下載。如果一個模型支援從 ModelScope 下載，模型資訊中的 Model Hubs"
" 這一項會包含 ModelScope。"
